{"title":"Classified 2x Goes Off-Road in Single 12sp Shimano/SRAM Cassette & Boost MTB Hubs","link":"https://bikerumor.com/classified-powershift-2x-internal-gear-mtb-hub-for-shimano-sram-12-speed/","date":1680603911000,"content":"<p>Classified’s two-speed internally geared Powershift hub brings 2x drivetrains back to mountain bikes with one new 12-speed MTB hub that works for both Shimano &amp; SRAM drivetrains, plus new Boost-spaced hubs and a tiny wireless thumb shifter. That’s right, with wireless electronic shifting and just one 11-40T Classified cassette, Powershift will bump up your MTB gearing range to 530% whether you are riding a Shimano 12sp or SRAM Eagle 1x drivetrain…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Classified Powershift 2x internal gear MTB hub for Shimano &amp; SRAM</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_-SRAM-Eagle.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_-SRAM-Eagle-800x450.jpg\" alt=\"Classified Powershift Boost MTB 2x internal gear mountain bike hub for Shimano or SRAM 12-speed, Bike Connection Agency photo by Rupert Fowler, SRAM drivetrain\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_-SRAM-Eagle-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_-SRAM-Eagle-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_-SRAM-Eagle-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_-SRAM-Eagle-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_-SRAM-Eagle-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_-SRAM-Eagle-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_-SRAM-Eagle-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_-SRAM-Eagle.jpg 2000w\" /></a><figcaption><em>c. Mountain Bike Connection Agency, photo by Rupert Fowler</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Much like we’ve seen on road and gravel, the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=classified+powershift\" target=\"_blank\">wireless Powershift hub</a> brings lightning-fast virtual front shifts back to modern 1x bikes with all the chainline and chain retention benefits of a single chainring setup, yet with the smaller gearing steps and wider overall gearing of a traditional 2x drivetrain. And you can shift under load while pedaling, to effectively drop or increase your gearing instantaneously like you would in 2 or 3 regular rear derailleur shifts. That’s especially helpful on the mountain bike when you will be coming out of a technical corner or hitting a steep technical climb, and can hit that instant gear shift…</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>What’s new?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_exploded-view.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_exploded-view-800x480.jpg\" alt=\"Classified Powershift Boost MTB 2x internal gear mountain bike hub for Shimano or SRAM 12-speed, Bike Connection Agency photo by Mirror Media, exploded view\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_exploded-view-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_exploded-view-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_exploded-view-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_exploded-view-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_exploded-view-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_exploded-view.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption><em>c. BCA, photo by Mirror Media</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Inside, the Classified Powershift MTB hub is <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/found-classified-wireless-internal-gear-hub-shifts-2x-range-on-your-1x-gravel-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">effectively unchanged</a>. Sure, Classified assures that the internals, axle, bearings &amp; seals have all been upgraded to handle the harder life of a mountain bike, but the functional bits are the same concept: a 1:0.68 ratio planetary reduction gear, a wireless electronic controller in the end of the Smart axle that doesn’t need to be recharged, and a wireless remote shifter that you can neatly integrate into your existing cockpit setup.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cnc-machined-steel-11-40T-cassette.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cnc-machined-steel-11-40T-cassette-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"Classified Powershift Boost MTB 2x internal gear mountain bike hub for Shimano or SRAM 12-speed, Bike Connection Agency photo by Mirror Media, 11-40T cassette\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cnc-machined-steel-11-40T-cassette-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cnc-machined-steel-11-40T-cassette-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cnc-machined-steel-11-40T-cassette-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cnc-machined-steel-11-40T-cassette-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cnc-machined-steel-11-40T-cassette-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cnc-machined-steel-11-40T-cassette.jpg 2000w\" /></a><figcaption><em>c. BCA, photo by Mirror Media</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The most obvious new bit is Classified’s new proprietary one-piece machined steel 11-40T cassette that works with both Shimano 12sp and SRAM Eagle 12sp derailleurs and chains. Classified says it is a happy medium between the two drivetrains, and while it takes a little bit more finetuning for its initial setup, once tuned they say it shifts great with either drivetrain. Pairing the 11-40T cassette with the internal reduction gear allows mountain bikers to size up their chainring by about 10-15% while getting both easier AND harder gears thanks to the system’s broad 530% gearing range.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cassette-profile.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cassette-profile-800x400.jpg\" alt=\"Classified Powershift Boost MTB 2x internal gear mountain bike hub for Shimano or SRAM 12-speed, Bike Connection Agency photo by Mirror Media, 11-40T cassette\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cassette-profile-800x400.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cassette-profile-297x149.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cassette-profile-120x60.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cassette-profile-768x384.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cassette-profile-1536x768.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_cassette-profile.jpg 1800w\" /></a><figcaption><em>c. BCA, photo by Mirror Media</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Important to note: the new 10-40T cassette is also compatible with the original 12x142mm Classified Powershift hub bringing bigger <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/classified-powershift-hub-goes-12-speed-for-sram-2x12-gearing-without-a-front-derailleur/\" target=\"_blank\">12sp gravel gearing</a> options to existing users, too.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Ringshifter-riding.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"444\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Ringshifter-riding-800x444.jpg\" alt=\"Classified Powershift Boost MTB 2x internal gear mountain bike hub for Shimano or SRAM 12-speed, Ringshifter\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Ringshifter-riding-800x444.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Ringshifter-riding-297x165.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Ringshifter-riding-120x67.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Ringshifter-riding-768x427.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Ringshifter-riding-1536x853.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Ringshifter-riding.jpg 1800w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The other big new thing is the tiny Ringshifter remote… not so unlike the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/zirbel-electronic-twist-shifters-signal-sram-axs-derailleurs-droppers-or-your-phone/\" target=\"_blank\">Zirbel</a> twist shifter in practice – just spin the paddle with your thumb to shift. But the Classified Ringshifter remote is completely self-contained and wireless – and rechargeable with a proprietary USB dongle after 10k shifts – making it incredibly quick to install in between your grip and brakes.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Powershuft-ready-hub.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Powershuft-ready-hub-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"Classified Powershift Boost MTB 2x internal gear mountain bike hub for Shimano or SRAM 12-speed, Bike Connection Agency photo by Mirror Media, empty Powershift-ready hubshell\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Powershuft-ready-hub-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Powershuft-ready-hub-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Powershuft-ready-hub-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Powershuft-ready-hub-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Powershuft-ready-hub-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Powershuft-ready-hub-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Powershuft-ready-hub.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption><em>c. BCA, photo by Mirror Media</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also new but pretty obvious, the new MTB system is Boost spaced, which means it isn’t a direct swap with other Powershift internals. But you do get wider rear hub &amp; 12x148mm axle spacing, wider bearing spacing, and compatibility with almost all modern mountain bikes.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_gear-ration-comaprison.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"444\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_gear-ration-comaprison-800x444.jpg\" alt=\"Classified Powershift Boost MTB 2x internal gear mountain bike hub for Shimano or SRAM 12-speed, gear ratio comparison\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_gear-ration-comaprison-800x444.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_gear-ration-comaprison-297x165.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_gear-ration-comaprison-120x67.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_gear-ration-comaprison-768x427.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_gear-ration-comaprison-1536x853.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_gear-ration-comaprison.jpg 1800w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Classified says Powershift MTB 12sp delivers 16 unique gears (<em>after factoring out duplicate ratios</em>) with a bit of a combination of derailleur &amp; hub shifting. That’s with the ‘new’ gears effectively in the middle of the cassette block for better chainline, and larger cogs/chainrings overall (more teeth) for improved drivetrain rolling efficiency. They say those bigger cogs and the fact that the cassette is machined steel also mean longer drivetrain durability.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_tech-dwgs-scaled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_tech-dwgs-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Classified Powershift Boost MTB 2x internal gear mountain bike hub for Shimano or SRAM 12-speed, tech drawings\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_tech-dwgs-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_tech-dwgs-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_tech-dwgs-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_tech-dwgs-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_tech-dwgs-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_tech-dwgs-2048x1364.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_tech-dwgs-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Weights for the system are claimed at 485g for the Powershift Boost MTB internal gear hub, 72g for the Smart axle, 125g for the 28-hole straight-pull centerlock disc brake hub shell OR 165g for the 32h j-bend 6-bolt disc shell, 24g for the Bluetooth Ringshifter, and 248g for the 12-speed 11-40T cassette. The Shimano AND SRAM compatible cassette includes the following gear steps: 11-12-13-14-15-17-19-22-25-29-34-40.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Interestingly weight-wise, Classified compares their complete Powershift setup with their own wheelset (including internally geared hub, cassette, shifter &amp; all installation hardware) at 2151g as quite comparable to a Shimano XT (2053g) or SRAM GX (2035g) setup with a light DT Swiss XRC 1501 carbon wheelset and the stock cassettes with more limited gearing. (<em>That does not include the Classified Smart axle relative to a standard thru-axle which likely adds around 50g extra.</em>)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Classified Powershift MTB – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_detail-800x480.jpg\" alt=\"Classified Powershift Boost MTB 2x internal gear mountain bike hub for Shimano or SRAM 12-speed, Bike Connection Agency photo by Rupert Fowler, detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_detail-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_detail-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_detail-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_detail-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_detail-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Rupert-Fowler_detail.jpg 2000w\" /></a><figcaption><em>c. BCA, photo by Rupert Fowler</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Like the road &amp; gravel Classified Powershift, the new MTB version will be available in several different ways. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Classified-pre-built-carbon-wheelset.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Classified-pre-built-carbon-wheelset-800x480.jpg\" alt=\"Classified Powershift Boost MTB 2x internal gear mountain bike hub for Shimano or SRAM 12-speed, Bike Connection Agency photo by Mirror Media, wheelset\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Classified-pre-built-carbon-wheelset-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Classified-pre-built-carbon-wheelset-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Classified-pre-built-carbon-wheelset-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Classified-pre-built-carbon-wheelset-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Classified-pre-built-carbon-wheelset-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_Classified-pre-built-carbon-wheelset.jpg 2000w\" /></a><figcaption><em>c. BCA, photo by Mirror Media</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can get a pre-built carbon XC wheelset from Classified for 2700€ with the complete Powershift MTB setup, or you can buy a Classified Powershift-ready wheelset from other wheelbuilders and then add on the 1450€ Powershift hub, cassette &amp; shifter kit, or for 1550€ you can buy the complete kit including the Powershift-ready hubshell itself so your local wheelbuilder can lace it into a custom wheel ready to add in the Classified tech.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_centerlock-hub.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_centerlock-hub-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"Classified Powershift Boost MTB 2x internal gear mountain bike hub for Shimano or SRAM 12-speed, Bike Connection Agency photo by Mirror Media, centerlock hub\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_centerlock-hub-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_centerlock-hub-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_centerlock-hub-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_centerlock-hub-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_centerlock-hub-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_centerlock-hub-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_centerlock-hub.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption><em>c. BCA, photo by Mirror Media</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So when can you actually get it? </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_SRAM-Eagle-chain.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_SRAM-Eagle-chain-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"Classified Powershift Boost MTB 2x internal gear mountain bike hub for Shimano or SRAM 12-speed, Bike Connection Agency photo by Mirror Media, Eagle chain\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_SRAM-Eagle-chain-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_SRAM-Eagle-chain-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_SRAM-Eagle-chain-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_SRAM-Eagle-chain-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_SRAM-Eagle-chain-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_SRAM-Eagle-chain-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Classified-Powershift-Boost-MTB-2x-internal-gear-mountain-bike-hub-for-Shimano-SRAM-12sp_Mountain-Bike-Connection-Winter_Mirror-Media_SRAM-Eagle-chain.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption><em>c. BCA, photo by Mirror Media</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Officially, Classified Powershift MTB launches today at the start of April, but real component availability is expected in about six weeks’ time, starting from May 23rd, 2023.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.classified-cycling.cc/\" target=\"_blank\">Classified-cycling.cc</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/classified-powershift-2x-internal-gear-mtb-hub-for-shimano-sram-12-speed/\">Classified 2x Goes Off-Road in Single 12sp Shimano/SRAM Cassette &amp; Boost MTB Hubs</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"58ee56df6cbca9fb1457449661e09c866e540eebaae82eda213c7ee1750ce08a","category":"Cycling"}